  "description": "This image captures a nighttime scene of a harbor or marina with boats, likely sailboats, illuminated with warm, golden lights. The lights create long streaks and reflections on the water's surface, suggesting movement and a long exposure shot. The boats are silhouetted against a dark, deep blue night sky. The lower portion of the image is dominated by darker, muted tones of the water and the base of the boats, while the upper section features the bright, elongated light trails and the dark outline of the masts and rigging. There is a soft glow emanating from the lights, creating a dreamy and ethereal atmosphere. The overall impression is one of tranquility and the gentle sway of boats at night.",
